wikipedia_page.main: Eleanor Jane Faulkner (born 5 January 1993) is an English competitive swimmer who represented Great Britain in the Olympic Games, and England in the Commonwealth Games.  At the 2012 Summer Olympics, she competed in the women's 800-metre freestyle, finishing in 22nd place overall in the heats, and not advancing to the final.
